Anyone who has read about or worked with a simulated double pendulum will
enjoy the video here, where a robot swings a double pendulum up from a
hanging start, balances it, and then resists slight external pokes:
 
http://hackaday.com/2010/11/27/balancing-inverted-pendulums/
